Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.37,0:02:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the pirates who are \Nafter the One Piece...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.74,0:02:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...head for the New World,\N the second half of the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.08,0:03:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, no one has ever fully explored it
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.32,0:03:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,except for Gold Roger, King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.44,0:03:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The New World has ruined many \Npirates' dreams and ambitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.48,0:03:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Monkey D. Luffy,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.22,0:03:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a boy whose body turned to rubber
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.06,0:03:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.61,0:03:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and his friends venture into that sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.11,0:03:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.69,0:03:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After surviving a fierce battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.19,0:03:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Straw Hats finally\N entered the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.01,0:03:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the harshest sea ruled\N by the Four Emperors.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.03,0:03:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They landed on Punk Hazard;
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.51,0:03:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,an island with two parts,\N one burning, the other frozen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.36,0:03:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After learning about the ruler of the island -\N Caesar Clown, aka the Master's motive,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.41,0:03:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and all while trying to escape Shinokuni,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.66,0:03:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,along with their pirate ally -
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.29,0:03:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Warlord - Trafalgar Law,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.84,0:03:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they are on the move to kidnap Caesar,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.96,0:03:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,save the children,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.34,0:03:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and escape from the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.54,0:04:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you just say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.64,0:04:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.49,0:04:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.16,0:04:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A Small Dragon!\N Momonosuke Appears!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.48,0:04:30.99,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Momonosuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.16,0:04:34.83,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(600,1)}THE BASEMENT OF C BUILDING -\N A GARBAGE DUMP LUFFY'S GROUP
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.99,0:04:33.10,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,That is my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.83,0:04:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that name before somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.40,0:04:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.02,0:04:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.96,0:04:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be somebody else.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.39,0:04:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.60,0:04:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...stop drooling!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.10,0:04:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't eat me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.31,0:04:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you try to eat me,\N I'll eat you first!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.08,0:04:59.92,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Behave yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.40,0:05:02.57,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1)}MOMONOSUKE (DRAGON)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.91,0:05:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.58,0:05:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe "Momonosuke" is\N stuck on a dragon's body
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.47,0:05:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and he's talking with his farts...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.19,0:05:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.40,0:05:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.25,0:05:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.53,0:05:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's torn in half! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.99,0:05:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm finally separated from it-bu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.39,0:05:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not talking with my farts!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.30,0:05:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.68,0:05:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.89,0:05:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, that dragon
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.01,0:05:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was bigger
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.84,0:05:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and we already ate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.01,0:05:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you then?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.60,0:05:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.91,0:05:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An eel is talking to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.82,0:05:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop drooling!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.90,0:05:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not an eel!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.12,0:05:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're starving, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.39,0:05:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.93,0:06:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Samurai warriors don't get hungry
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.00,0:06:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,after just ten days of fasting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.55,0:06:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten days?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.70,0:06:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you and\N why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.42,0:06:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.98,0:06:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become\N the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.02,0:06:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-P-P-P...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.54,0:06:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.81,0:06:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be joking.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.29,0:06:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirates are big, heavyweight men.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.81,0:06:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are more violent and strong-looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.20,0:06:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, eel, how can I get out of...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.78,0:06:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Momonosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.44,0:06:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're from somewhere\N else, too, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.47,0:06:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All I know is there are\N so many sick children here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.02,0:06:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even know what kind of island \Nthis is and what happened to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.08,0:07:05.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It all began when I happened \Nto stow away on a ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.58,0:07:11.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I tried not to be so friendly
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.76,0:07:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but those children were kind to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.49,0:07:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're giving out food.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.06,0:07:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.29,0:07:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.68,0:07:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want any!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.21,0:07:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am a samurai!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.52,0:07:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't accept alms!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.30,0:07:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were very nice to me
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.38,0:07:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I was on edge so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.57,0:07:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got you some food.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.82,0:07:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said I don't want any!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.14,0:07:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You better eat something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.02,0:07:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're all separated from parents \Nso we must stick together...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.57,0:07:49.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody can understand how I feel!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.16,0:07:59.62,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1)}THE BISCUIT ROOM
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.19,0:08:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am "Master" Caesar!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.28,0:08:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on in!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.21,0:08:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is your playground from today!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.27,0:08:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are many giant children!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.23,0:08:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they sick, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.32,0:08:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can count on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.57,0:08:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll treat you all at any cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.60,0:08:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.08,0:08:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're all friends from today!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.43,0:08:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.65,0:08:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.97,0:08:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.65,0:08:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.33,0:08:33.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a name.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.15,0:08:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.91,0:08:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have some snacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.19,0:08:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want any!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.47,0:08:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Candy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.60,0:08:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want any!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.13,0:08:55.59,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1)}A FEW DAYS LATER
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.83,0:08:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, is it true that one of the kids escaped?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.11,0:09:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes but everybody on the \Nboarding list was accounted for.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.87,0:09:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.77,0:09:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case,\N let's split up and search.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.97,0:09:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can I get out of here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.30,0:10:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.09,0:10:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were on the same ship with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.81,0:10:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.37,0:10:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so your name is Momonosuke-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.25,0:10:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a "secret room"\N where no one is allowed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.70,0:10:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.59,0:10:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get involved with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.18,0:10:58.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.61,0:10:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.68,0:11:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no reason!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.69,0:11:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just looking for an exit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.22,0:11:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.23,0:11:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is something I need to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.51,0:11:13.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know it's hard but every child here \Nis going through the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.09,0:11:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody wants to see his or her \Nfather and mother as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.49,0:11:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of us came here from\N different islands to be treated
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.58,0:11:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but everybody feels the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.99,0:11:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are so many things I wanna do
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.92,0:11:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if I could just get back home!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.97,0:11:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody is friendly at the \NBiscuit Room and it's fun there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.00,0:11:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can forget the pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.07,0:11:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So why don't you eat \Nsomething, Momonosuke-kun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.17,0:11:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.09,0:11:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.99,0:11:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.81,0:11:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, somebody's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.28,0:11:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Momonosuke-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.37,0:11:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The door to the secret room is open!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.79,0:12:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.41,0:12:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.30,0:12:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.17,0:12:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anybody there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.39,0:12:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.03,0:12:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.07,0:12:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A d-dragon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.49,0:12:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.96,0:12:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.56,0:13:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Momonosuke-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.53,0:13:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.58,0:13:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I remember correctly,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.57,0:13:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there was a man-made Devil \NFruit that Vegapunk created here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.69,0:13:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard it was a failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.95,0:13:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I heard so, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.98,0:13:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That pain in my chest I felt suddenly -
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.32,0:13:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought my heart was gonna explode!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.34,0:13:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had trouble running before.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.17,0:13:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.47,0:14:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I am originally a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.81,0:14:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You ate a Devil Fruit, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.98,0:14:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it made you an eel man, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.61,0:14:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eels don't have horns.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.65,0:14:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why don't you turn \Nyourself back into a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.25,0:14:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.36,0:14:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I can turn myself back to myself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.87,0:14:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.06,0:14:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.51,0:14:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a Zoan-type.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.59,0:14:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, I wonder\N how high this ceiling is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.77,0:14:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't even see the hole\N that I fell through.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.58,0:14:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to get out of here, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.16,0:14:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and tell those children the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.10,0:14:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I happened to hear something!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.75,0:14:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Caesar guy was talking...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.29,0:15:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have another group\N of good obedient kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.12,0:15:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The other kids are growing\N bigger without problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.68,0:15:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, after all, this is an experiment \Nto see the limitations of drug dosing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.18,0:15:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think they can take it that long.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.02,0:15:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I assume they'll all be dead in five years.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.62,0:15:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we need to find more kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.13,0:15:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, experiments come with failures.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.07,0:15:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a necessary sacrifice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.29,0:15:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those stupid kids can help \Nthe world's greatest scientist -
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.70,0:15:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master Caesar Clown
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.37,0:15:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and do good for the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.74,0:15:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's a short life,\N they have to be happy with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.32,0:15:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.06,0:16:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought he was a doctor
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.12,0:16:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but he is actually a bad man
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.74,0:16:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who is going to let the children die!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.44,0:16:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the kids have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.67,0:16:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.07,0:16:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have some snacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.57,0:16:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know it's hard but every child here \Nis going through the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.53,0:16:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody wants to see his or her \Nfather and mother as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.53,0:16:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel sorry for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.41,0:16:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't do anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.69,0:16:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should be ashamed of \Nmyself as a samurai warrior!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.65,0:16:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was on my way to tell the\N children but I fell down here
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.09,0:16:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when I tried to hide in a trash can.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.73,0:16:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Caesar!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.97,0:16:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, Momo,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.18,0:16:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna climb up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.13,0:16:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take you with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.50,0:16:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.26,0:16:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are you gonna climb that high?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.38,0:17:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna climb the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.46,0:17:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold onto me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.58,0:17:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.87,0:17:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about the children.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.68,0:17:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My friends are on their way to help them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.53,0:17:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.10,0:17:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They always keep their word!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.24,0:17:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.24,0:17:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.64,0:17:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What I thought was right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.20,0:17:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are not an ordinary...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.06,0:17:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.11,0:17:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.34,0:17:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.04,0:17:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you too hungry?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.37,0:17:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stay with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.70,0:17:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay with me! Stay with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.96,0:17:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stay with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.58,0:17:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay with me! Stay with me! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.52,0:17:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.64,0:17:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.30,0:17:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay with me! \NStay with me! Stay with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.69,0:18:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay with me!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.23,0:18:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.83,0:18:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.94,0:18:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's the matter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.21,0:18:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.58,0:18:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.24,0:18:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.09,0:18:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,flying!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.51,0:18:46.14,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1)}AT THE BACK OF 2ND FLOOR OF B BUILDING \NA PATH AT AN EXAMINATION ROOM
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.51,0:18:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Nami and the others \Nare doing okay without me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.97,0:18:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, at least Zoro is with them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.83,0:19:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll save you at any cost
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.15,0:19:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so wait for me, Momonosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.33,0:19:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brook!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.48,0:19:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me know if you see the
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.61,0:19:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sea Prism Stone handcuffs\N that Robin told us to find!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.50,0:19:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, corpse-dono!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.21,0:19:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to depend on your sorcery!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.61,0:19:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Count on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.57,0:19:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just need to look\N for samurai-san's son
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.53,0:19:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and some Sea Prism\N Stone handcuffs, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.74,0:19:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's check the other side of that wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.34,0:19:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was his name Momonosuke-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.73,0:19:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet he is a boy\N who dresses like samurai-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.81,0:19:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.57,0:19:43.91,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,1)}D BUILDING - THE "SAD" MANUFACTURING ROOM
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.57,0:19:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Armament Haki\N surpasses your ability by far.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.21,0:20:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you're smart enough to know
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.69,0:20:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that it's useless to fight against me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.16,0:20:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smoker.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.93,0:20:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or are you trying to avenge \Nthose dumb-asses' death?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.61,0:20:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're not gonna die that easily -
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.74,0:20:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they're not that weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.87,0:20:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though they're misfits,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.98,0:20:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they're still Navy soldiers!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.60,0:20:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shave!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.34,0:20:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mess with the Navy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.74,0:21:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know you cared\N so much about your men,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.65,0:21:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smoker-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.50,0:21:17.17,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(550,1)}B BUILDING - NEAR THE BISCUIT ROOM
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.73,0:21:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody, this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.26,0:21:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get to the Biscuit Room\N where the children are!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.67,0:21:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.72,0:21:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are too slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.34,0:21:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The deadly gas is right behind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.12,0:21:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't wanna die, run faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.06,0:21:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.06,0:21:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.60,0:21:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, don't kick me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.89,0:21:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch, brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.15,0:21:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.01,0:21:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.44,0:21:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't kick me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.57,0:21:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.61,0:21:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Black Foot brother is gonna \Nkill us before the deadly gas does!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.53,0:21:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be a baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.81,0:21:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.89,0:21:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.89,0:21:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you wanna save the children,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.73,0:22:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,go to the Biscuit Room now!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.54,0:22:04.34,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1)}B BUILDING 3RD FLOOR - THE BISCUIT ROOM
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.13,0:22:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's cold! The whole\N room is in a blizzard!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.20,0:22:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just took off my coat!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.41,0:22:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is a Snow-Snow Fruit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.41,0:22:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn that snow woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.01,0:22:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.84,0:22:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't eat the candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.88,0:22:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mocha, run!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.77,0:22:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Mocha!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.77,0:22:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give us the candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.68,0:22:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! You all have to\N come to your senses!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.71,0:22:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't have it all to yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.72,0:22:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop running!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.03,0:22:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try to hold them,\N if even for a little while.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.18,0:22:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.38,0:22:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.07,0:22:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alright, Robin?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.35,0:22:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.65,0:23:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Pirate Hunter Zoro
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.82,0:23:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with a 120 million berry bounty!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.19,0:23:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You three, go stop those kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.00,0:23:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a Logia-type.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.51,0:23:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take care of her!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.64,0:23:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even while he's at the mercy of Monet's ability to freely manipulate snow,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.09,0:23:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro still tries to let Nami and the others \Nescape, despite the relentless attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.72,0:23:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's then that Monet transforms \Ninto a terrifying monster
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.89,0:23:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the situation worsens.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.26,0:23:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The crew find themselves backed into a corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.98,0:23:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.45,0:23:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A Deadly Fight in a Blizzard!\N The Straw Hats vs. the Snow Woman!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.69,0:23:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.98,0:23:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
